{"tid":1962742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥兌現承諾，所有非香港人醫治中國武漢肺炎由政府納稅人血汗埋單","createTime":"2020-04-07T16:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T03:58:27.000Z","uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3c14bc3a4418eaf6ca3f9b0cbcefd43a33ee3dc5","tid":1962742,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:20:30.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局向立法會財委會提交的文件指，截止二月底，有108位非符合資格人士入住公立醫院，接受新型冠狀病毒治療，當中104人已出院及1人死亡，這批人士中有22人仍未清繳醫療費用，涉及約20萬元。<br />\n<br />\n政府指，醫管局設有追討欠款機制，若病人出院後仍未清繳費用，當局會致電提醒病人或其家屬清繳賬單，病人在指定時間未繳清，醫管局會徵收行政費用；適當情況下亦會採取法律行動，包括入稟小額錢債審裁處或委託律師追收欠款。"},{"pid":"fee5adc944f58d2aa6e2057ec72a179fe1a22862","tid":1962742,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:27:18.000Z","msg":"小你老母錢債處咩，都拍拍屎忽過關走撚左啦"},{"pid":"5c5473830f2cc93a27a08a0f5d6b23c6c4712247","tid":1962742,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fee5adc944f58d2aa6e2057ec72a179fe1a22862","tid":1962742,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:27:18.000Z","msg":"小你老母錢債處咩，都拍拍屎忽過關走撚左啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T23:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536d6b1ea71184295cc794c517ab0d94265a684c","tid":1962742,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T03:58:27.000Z","msg":"推"}]}